    "Name": "Coriolis CRLS-386",
    "Details": "The CRLS-386 is the first Star League upgrade of the Coriolis, trading the original AC/10 for an LB-10X autocannon with cluster munition capability and adding an ER Large Laser for meaningful long-range presence. Double heat sinks manage the increased thermal load from the energy weapons. The AC/20 and jump jets remain, keeping the original close-range ambush capability fully intact while broadening the engagement envelope considerably.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - AC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
